%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Admin as Admin/API
  participant API as Go API
  participant EMQX as EMQX
  participant MQ as MQTT Broker
  actor FW as Firmware

  Admin->>API: Rotate device MQTT credentials\n(admin workflow)
  API->>EMQX: Update auth + ACL for device
  API-->>Admin: 200 rotation acknowledged

  Note over FW,MQ: Existing MQTT session may be dropped after rotation
  MQ-->>FW: Disconnect / auth failure
  FW->>API: GET /api/bootstrap?imei=...\n(header x-api-key)
  API-->>FW: New username/password + endpoints[]
  FW->>MQ: Reconnect using new creds
